v1.0.0.beta?
------------

 * Make 'monk' and 'monk help' appear more user-friendly. (rstacruz)

 * Add the 'monk version' command. (rstacruz)

 * Make the 'monk init' command show more detailed info with instructions on how to proceed next. (rstacruz)

 * Doing 'monk init' now caches the skeleton git files into `~/.cache/monk/`. (rstacruz)

 * Doing 'monk init' now warns you properly if the target path exists. (rstacruz)

 * Add the 'monk purge' command which cleans the Monk skeleton cache. (rstacruz)

 * Update the readme to remove legacy instructions and make a note of the new RVM dependency, and the 'monk install' command. (rstacruz)
